These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: aquamarine, turquise
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, software-developer
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, zinnia
2 different pets are kept: snake, mouse
1. the owner of the snake is not to the right of the software-developer##8
2. the software-developer is somewhere to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
3. the person who likes aquamarine is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Color      | turquise     | aquamarine      |
| Job          | software-developer | project-manager    |
| Flower         | zinnia   | balloon-flower |
| Pet   | snake  | mouse      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, marigold
2 different pets are kept: lizard, guinea-pig
2 different games are played: chess, go
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, papaya
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the person playing chess##5
3. the person playing go is not to the right of the person playing chess##8
4. the person eating cauliflower is not the owner of the guinea-pig##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Flower    | azalea        | marigold    |
| Pet       | lizard         | guinea-pig |
| Game         | go | chess   |
| Food   | cauliflower               | papaya  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different games are played: bridge, billiard
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, video-games
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, trike
There are 2 different favourite colors: coral, yellow
1. the person driving the airplane is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the trike is not to the right of the person who likes yellow##8
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the left of the person playing billiard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Game   | bridge       | billiard |
| Hobby   | fishing       | video-games    |
| Transport   | airplane | trike |
| Color           | coral        | yellow   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, february
2 different games are played: whist, billiard
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, tiparillo
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, folk
1. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
2. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the left of the fan of folk##8
3. the fan of folk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Birthday         | february | december  |
| Game           | billiard  | whist |
| Cigar   | tiparillo | alhambra   |
| Music-Genre     | folk   | d&b |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-5::.
House: craftsman, tower
2 different games are played: billiard, mah-jongg
There 2 different types of food: pepper, lettuce
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, hip-hop
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
2. the person eating pepper is not to the right of the person playing billiard##8
3. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| House   | craftsman | tower |
| Game   | mah-jongg    | billiard     |
| Food         | pepper  | lettuce    |
| Music-Genre     | hip-hop     | soul       |

