2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who likes white##1
3. the person who growssunflower is not to the right of the person playing monopoly##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |
| Game        | mah-jongg             | monopoly     |
| Beverage         | tea | almond-milk  |
| Color         | white           | lilac |
| Flower   | zinnia              | sunflower |

