The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, comedy
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, tea
1. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the left of the person who likes purple##8
2. the person drinking cola is the person drinking cola##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
4. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
5. the person drinking tea is not to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |         2          |
| Sport        | sailing | ice-hockey            |
| Color       | purple | red              |
| Movie-Genre         | martial-arts  | comedy |
| Beverage   | cola     | tea         |

